Determining outlier subjects

To investigate potential outlier subjects I fit the following glm to each subject: glm(is_error ~ feat_c * mask_c).

There are outliers in every term when the models are fit at the by-subject level. The dashed vertical lines depict the symmetric cutoff criteria for determining outlier subjects.
